Tyrol, Austria and in the Quebec City area, Canada, as well as the Prostate, 
Lung, Colorectal and Ovarian (PLCO) trial in the United States and the European 
Randomized Study of Screening for Prostate Cancer (ERSPC). In the meantime, 
individual case finding (opportunistic screening) is recommended for men with a 
life-expectancy of at least 10 years.

