clearly demonstrated, nor was any interaction observed with blood components.
CONCLUSIONS: Two of the new glucosylated derivatives of Gd-DTPA 
(Cd-DTPA-BC2-beta-cellobionA 2 and Gd-DTPA-BC4-beta-glucosylA 7) can be proposed 
as blood-pool MR contrast agents, considering their vascular remanence.

